<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Regenerate Skagit</title>

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f8f7f4;
        --text: #1f2933;
        --muted: #1f2933;
        --accent: #2f855a;
        --card-bg: #f1f3f0;
        --shadow: rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
      }

      main {
        max-width: 42rem;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1rem 3rem;
      }

      /* Header with background photo and overlay */
      header {
        position: relative;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        background: var(--card-bg) url("/assets/images/1jEpupgChO-960.webp") no-repeat center center;
        background-size: cover;
        border-radius: 1rem;
        box-shadow: 0 3px 8px var(--shadow);
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--text);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      header::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        background: rgba(248,247,244,0.6);
        /* semi-transparent overlay */
        border-radius: 1rem;
        z-index: 0;
      }

      header > * {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      header strong {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      h3 {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      p {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .muted {
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .card {
        background: var(--card-bg);
        border-radius: 1rem;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 3px 8px var(--shadow);
      }

      .values {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        background: var(--card-bg);
        padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 1px 5px var(--shadow);
        text-align: center;
      }

 .cta {
  position: relative; /* ← this is critical */
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 2rem;
  background: var(--card-bg) url("/assets/images/UQvFmhqMg3-960.webp") no-repeat center center;
  background-size: cover; /* ensures image scales nicely */
  border-radius: 1rem;
  padding: 2rem 1.5rem; /* make space for content */
  box-shadow: 0 3px 8px var(--shadow);
  color: white; /* optional if overlay is dark */
}

.cta::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
  background: rgba(248,247,244,0.6); /* semi-transparent overlay */
  border-radius: 1rem;
  z-index: 0; /* sits behind content */
}

/* ensure the content is above the overlay */
.cta > * {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

      .cta a {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
        background: var(--accent);

        color: white;
        border-radius: 0.6rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
      }
      .cta a:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        background: #2b7c50;
      }

      footer {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        padding-top: 2rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        text-align: center;
      }
      footer a {
        margin: 0 0.5rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      @media(min-width:768px) {
        h1 {
          font-size: 2.4rem;
        }
        h2 {
          font-size: 1.6rem;
        }
        h3 {
          font-size: 1.25rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>

      <!-- Header Card with Background Photo -->
      <header>
        <strong>Regenerate Skagit</strong>
        <h1>A community rooted in the Skagit watershed.</h1>
        <p class="muted">
        Learning how to live well with land, water, and each other—locally and for the long term.
      </p>
        <div class="values">People first · Place-based · Long-term</div>
      </header>

      <!-- Meaning / Orientation Card -->
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Big systems feel distant and overwhelming.</h2>
        <p>
        Food systems, climate systems, economic systems—most are too large to see clearly or feel agency within.
      </p>

        <h3>Regeneration happens at human scale.</h3>
        <p>
        It grows through relationships, shared learning, and practical action grounded in place. 
        It starts with paying attention to where we live, who we live with, and how choices ripple through land and water.
      </p>

        <p>This is bioregional work: beginning with the watershed, the farms, the towns, and the people who share them.</p>

        <h3>You don’t have to agree with everything.<br>You just have to show up.</h3>
        <p>Regenerate Skagit brings people together to listen, learn, and practice living in better relationship with place and each other.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Card -->
      <div class="card cta">
        <h2>Get Involved</h2>
        <a href="/content/site/get-involved/">Get Involved</a>
        <p class="muted">Events, conversations, and ways to participate.<br>No expertise required.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <footer>
        <p>Rooted in the Skagit watershed, Cascadia.</p>
        <p>
          <a href="#">Contact</a>
          <a href="#">Newsletter</a>
          <a href="#">Instagram</a>
        </p>
      </footer>

    </main>
  </body>
</html>